"Policajca *su* zvali da obavi istragu." (They called the policeman to investigate.)
"Policajcu *je* rečeno da ide na mesto događaja." (The policeman was told to go to the scene of the incident.)
"Policajac *je* pronašao nove informacije." (The policeman found new information.)
"Policajci *su* počeli istragu." (The policemen began the investigation.)
"Policajcu *su* pružili pomoć." (They gave the policeman help.)
"Policajac *je* zapretio da će se obračunati sa zločincima." (The policeman threatened to deal with the criminals.)